trans-unit.source: Provides functionality for a stack of client channel sinks that must be invoked during an asynchronous message response decoding.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller funktioner för en grupp av klienten kanal sänkor som måste anropas under ett asynkront meddelande svar avkodning.

trans-unit.source: The IClientChannelSinkStack is used during processing of responses to asynchronous calls.
trans-unit.target: IClientChannelSinkStack används under bearbetning av svar på asynkrona anrop.

trans-unit.source: During a synchronous call, the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method is called when a message is outbound to the server.
trans-unit.target: Under en synkrona anrop i <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden anropas när ett meddelande är utgående till servern.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Each sink in the sink chain calls the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A> method on the next sink until the call reaches the transport sink at the end of the chain.
trans-unit.target: Varje mottagare i kedjan-anrop som tar emot den <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A>metoden på nästa sink tills anropet transportmottagaren i slutet av kedjan.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A>

trans-unit.source: From there the message is transported to the server.

When the formatter sink is called through the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMessageSink.AsyncProcessMessage%2A> method, it dispatches the call asynchronously by calling <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A> on the next channel sink.
trans-unit.target: När formaterare sink anropas via den <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMessageSink.AsyncProcessMessage%2A>metoden skickar den anropet asynkront genom att anropa <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A>i nästa kanalmottagaren.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A> </xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMessageSink.AsyncProcessMessage%2A>

trans-unit.source: A stack of reply sinks is needed to process the response.
trans-unit.target: En hög svar sänkor behövs för att bearbeta svaret.

trans-unit.source: Any sink that wants to process the response needs to push itself to the client channel sink stack inside of <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Alla mottagare som du vill ska bearbeta svaret måste push sig till klienten kanalmottagarstack inuti <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A>.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: Pops the information associated with all the sinks from the sink stack up to and including the specified sink.
trans-unit.target: Visas information som är associerade med alla sänkor från mottagarstacken upp till och inklusive angivna sink.

trans-unit.source: The sink to remove and return from the sink stack.
trans-unit.target: Ta bort och returnera från mottagarstacken mottagare.

trans-unit.source: Information generated on the request side and associated with the specified sink.
trans-unit.target: Informationen genereras på begäran-sidan och som är associerade med den angivna sinken.

trans-unit.source: The immediate caller does not have infrastructure permission.
trans-unit.target: Den omedelbara anroparen har inte behörighet för infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: Pushes the specified sink and information associated with it onto the sink stack.
trans-unit.target: Push-meddelanden angivna sink och associerad till mottagarstacken information.

trans-unit.source: The information generated on the request side and specified in the `state` parameter is returned in the `state` parameter of the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessResponse%2A> method on the corresponding sink.
trans-unit.target: Informationen genereras på begäran-sidan och anges i den `state` parametern returneras den `state` parameter för den <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessResponse%2A>metoden på motsvarande sink.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessResponse%2A>

trans-unit.source: The sink to push onto the sink stack.
Information generated on the request side that is needed on the response side.
trans-unit.target: Information som skapats på begäran-sida som krävs på sidan svar.

trans-unit.source: The immediate caller does not have infrastructure permission.
trans-unit.target: Den omedelbara anroparen har inte behörighet för infrastruktur.
